Fact: Working out can reduce overall fat, but you can’t control what part of your body burns the most fat. Your body breaks down fat and uses it as fuel when you exercise. But your body’s not picky. 
 
It’ll burn fat from anywhere in your body, not just the part you’re working the most.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lLfmq8O.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Myth:  We have five senses

Fact: Besides the five empirical senses, sight, sound, touch, taste and smell, there are at least four other senses that are rarely cited 

proprioception—sensing one's orientation in space 

thermoception—sense of temperature

equilibrioception—sense of balance

interoception—sense of one's physiological condition.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lzcmiAw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It's a myth that: Bulls become angry when they see the color red. 

Fact: It's not the color of the cape that angers the bull but it’s the movement of the cape. We know this based on many experiments with different colored capes being stationary and being moved and the bull favored movement over the color of the cape every time. 

We also know that bulls are actually red-green colorblind and would have a hard time distinguishing red from green, orange, and brown.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tAXIt1d.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Myth: Marie Antoinette is quoted as having famously said "let them eat cake".

Fact: There's zero evidence that she ever said it or something like it. The original claim was that she said the peasants should eat brioche. 

But there are examples from earlier folklore where oblivious aristocrats show their ignorance by telling the starving poor to simply eat rich luxurious cake.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/clYdoyX.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It's a myth that: Penis size varies according to race. 

Fact: This idea is not supported by scientific evidence. According to a urologist named Aaron Spitz, many studies and websites promoting variation of penis size between races use unscientific methods of collecting information (such as self-reporting which is very unreliable), and often ignore contradictory evidence. https://www.dailydot.com/irl/penis-size-infographic-debunked/</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/e3A4UnR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Myth: A penny dropped from the empire state building can kill a person on the sidewalk

Fact: According to the myth the penny would accelerate to the point that it could kill a person on the sidewalk below. But in reality, the penny will reach terminal velocity of about 30-100 miles per hour depending on the wind. If you dropped a penny from up there it might hurt, but it wouldn't kill anyone.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QXPWWOD.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It's a myth that: Goldfish have a 3-7 second memory 

Fact: Goldfish can learn basic survival skills and remember them for up to three months. They can even tell time. In lab tests they could be conditioned to push a lever for food at roughly the same time each day.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7jB6DLP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Myth: Vikings wore horns on their helmets.

Fact: Most vikings never did. Some of them may have had horns affixed to their gear, but they mostly had normal metal helmets. Wagner's 1876 opera The Ring of Nibelung popularized this image into our minds.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CiVKUNU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It's a myth that: You should wait 24 hours before reporting a missing person.

Fact: There is no need to wait 24 hours, at least not anymore. Call 911. In fact, taking action within the first 48 hours is crucial to bringing a missing child home. 

The No. 1 biggest problem is that family members wait too long to report a missing persons case. You lose valuable time during those 24 hours.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IXWMmLB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Myth: The ingredients in COVID-19 vaccines are dangerous.

Fact: Nearly all the ingredients in COVID-19 vaccines are also ingredients in many foods – fats, sugars, and salts. Exact vaccine ingredients vary by manufacturer. COVID-19 vaccines do NOT contain ingredients like preservatives, tissues (like aborted fetal cells), antibiotics, food proteins, medicines, latex, or metals.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ZgBCZ8l</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[EnglightenMe]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Gonna need a looooot more motivation than that</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Rog6Btl</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qIRV2vF.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Rog6Btl</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TiptronicS]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>A moderately sized DK dump of stolen memes for these trying times 622.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/CL6TTl2</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3Ypu3y5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OJ84bVy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vOmrgv4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Q1oMpUz.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fKUKVwz.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3wO8xpQ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Fcgd6Xx.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cvxkIGS.jpg" style="max-width: 90